\s Joyful Thanksgiving
\p
\v 1 \w  In that  |strong="1931" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.3" \w* \w  day  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.2" \w* \w  you will say :  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.1" \w* \w  “ O LORD ,  |strong="3068" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.5" \w* \w  I will praise You .  |strong="3034" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.4" \w* \w  Although  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.6" \w* \w  You were angry  |strong="599" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.7" \w* \w  with me ,  |srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.8" \w* \w  Your anger  |strong="639" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.10" \w* \w  has turned away ,  |strong="7725" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.9" \w* \w  and You have comforted me .  |strong="5162" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.1.11" \w* \v 2 \w  Surely  |strong="2009" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.1" \w* \w  God  |strong="410" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.2" \w* \w  is my salvation ;  |strong="3444" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.3" \w* \w  I will trust  |strong="982" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.4" \w* \w  and not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.5" \w* \w  be afraid .  |strong="6342" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.6" \w* \w  For  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.7" \w* \w  the LORD  |strong="3050" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.10" \w* \w  GOD  |strong="3068" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.11" \w* \w  is my strength  |strong="5797" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.8" \w* \w  and my song ,  |strong="2176" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.9" \w* \w  and He also has become  |strong="1961" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.12" \w* \w  my  |srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.13" \w* \w  salvation . ”  |strong="3444" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.2.14" \w* \v 3 \w  With joy  |strong="8342" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.3.3" \w* \w  you will draw  |strong="7579" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.3.1" \w* \w  water  |strong="4325" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.3.2" \w* \w  from the springs  |strong="4599" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.3.4" \w* \w  of salvation ,  |strong="3444" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.3.5" \w* \v 4 \w  and on that  |strong="1931" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.4.3" \w* \w  day  |strong="3117" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.4.2" \w* \w  you will say :  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:ISA.12.4.1" \w* \w  “ Give praise  |strong="3034" 