.13.9.14" \w* \v 10 \w  For  |strong="3588" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.1" \w* \w  the stars  |strong="3556" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.2" \w* \w  of heaven  |strong="8064" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.3" \w* \w  and their constellations  |strong="3685" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.4" \w* \w  will not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.5" \w* \w  give  |strong="1984" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.6" \w* \w  their light .  |strong="216" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.7" \w* \w  The rising  |strong="3318" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.10" \w* \w  sun  |strong="8121" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.9" \w* \w  will be darkened ,  |strong="2821" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.8" \w* \w  and the moon  |strong="3394" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.11" \w* \w  will not  |strong="3808" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.12" \w* \w  give  |strong="5050" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.13" \w* \w  its light .  |strong="216" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.10.14" \w* \v 11 \w  I will punish  |strong="6485" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.1" \w* \w  the world  |strong="8398" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.3" \w*   \add for its\add* \w  evil  |strong="7451" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.4" \w* \w  and  |strong="5921" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.5" \w* \w  the wicked  |strong="7563" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.6" \w* \w  for their iniquity .  |strong="5771" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.7" \w* \w  I will end  |strong="7673" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.8" \w* \w  the haughtiness  |strong="1347" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.9" \w* \w  of the arrogant  |strong="2086" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.10" \w* \w  and lay low  |strong="8213" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.13" \w* \w  the pride  |strong="1346" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.11" \w* \w  of the ruthless .  |strong="6184" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.11.12" \w* \v 12   I will make \w  man  |strong="582" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.12.2" \w* \w  scarcer  |strong="3365" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.12.1" \w* \w  than pure gold ,  |strong="6337" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.12.3" \w* \w  and mankind  |strong="120" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.12.4" \w* \w  rarer than the gold  |strong="3800" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.12.5" \w* \w  of Ophir .  |strong="211" srcloc="WLC:ISA.13.12